GADADHARA PANDIT: Huh?

00:05:57.060 --> 00:05:57.726
AUDIENCE: Noise.

00:05:57.726 --> 00:05:58.260
Noise.

00:05:58.260 --> 00:05:58.490
GADADHARA PANDIT: Noise.

