OK.

00:06:03.650 --> 00:06:06.457
What else?

00:06:06.457 --> 00:06:07.290
AUDIENCE: Commuting.

00:06:07.290 --> 00:06:07.575
GADADHARA PANDIT: OK.

00:06:07.575 --> 00:06:09.610
Yeah, that's going
to be stressful.

00:06:09.610 --> 00:06:10.621
Anything else?

