00:37:30.320 --> 00:37:36.690
So the next thing, one of
the most important things

00:37:36.690 --> 00:37:40.420
about dealing with stress,
because stress is in the mind.

00:37:40.420 --> 00:37:42.080
It's happening up here.

00:37:42.080 --> 00:37:46.030
We talked about all the ways
the mind creates our reality.

00:37:46.030 --> 00:37:49.610
So now we're going to talk about
something that directly deals

00:37:49.610 --> 00:37:55.770
with your mind, goes to the
very source of where stress is,

00:37:55.770 --> 00:37:58.610
and creates a healthy
environment for where

00:37:58.610 --> 00:38:00.185
all of these items
are processed.

