Psychology Today-- helps you
decrease anxiety, depression,

00:38:58.810 --> 00:39:01.010
and stress.

00:39:01.010 --> 00:39:04.810
Because again, all of these
things are happening up here.

00:39:04.810 --> 00:39:08.640
You don't want them to happen,
but the mind makes it happen.

00:39:08.640 --> 00:39:11.260
The mind makes it real.

00:39:11.260 --> 00:39:12.920
That's what's really happening.

