00:43:10.340 --> 00:43:13.220
But we will do some
breathing and meditation.

00:43:13.220 --> 00:43:18.110
So having said all that, we can
do some meditation right now.

00:43:18.110 --> 00:43:20.190
And then I'll open
it up for questions.

00:43:20.190 --> 00:43:21.834
That sound OK?

00:43:21.834 --> 00:43:22.740
All right.

00:43:22.740 --> 00:43:26.336
So if you can go ahead
and again sit comfortably.

00:43:26.336 --> 00:43:29.752
What's the time?

00:43:29.752 --> 00:43:30.728
Ten minutes.

00:43:34.144 --> 00:43:36.110
OK.

00:43:36.110 --> 00:43:37.190
You can close your eyes.

00:43:43.840 --> 00:43:48.820
And for now don't worry about
what you're going to do later.

00:43:48.820 --> 00:43:51.020
Try not to think about
what happened yesterday

00:43:51.020 --> 00:43:52.480
or last week.

00:43:52.480 --> 00:43:55.180
Just feel your body
sitting in its chair come

00:43:55.180 --> 00:43:56.180
into the present moment.

00:44:03.500 --> 00:44:07.210
And take a deep breath
in through your nose,

00:44:07.210 --> 00:44:08.120
filling your lungs.

00:44:13.510 --> 00:44:16.480
And exhale deeply, completely.

00:44:21.000 --> 00:44:24.100
Now we're going to do a
countdown of our breathing,

00:44:24.100 --> 00:44:27.800
keeping our mind focused on our
breath even when it wanders.

00:44:27.800 --> 00:44:29.010
Inhale 10.

00:44:32.790 --> 00:44:35.830
Complete inhale.

00:44:35.830 --> 00:44:38.440
When your lungs are
filled, exhale 10.

00:44:45.670 --> 00:44:47.320
Exhale completely.

00:44:47.320 --> 00:44:48.330
Inhale nine.

00:44:55.710 --> 00:44:57.480
Exhale nine.

00:45:07.380 --> 00:45:09.095
Inhale eight.

00:45:16.470 --> 00:45:18.310
Exhale eight.

00:45:18.310 --> 00:45:19.610
Stay focused on your breathing.

00:45:23.600 --> 00:45:27.750
Now continue breathing and
counting down on your own

00:45:27.750 --> 00:45:29.590
till you get to one.

00:45:29.590 --> 00:45:31.750
As your mind wanders,
keep it on the breath.

00:46:10.620 --> 00:46:13.190
Stay focused on your breath.

00:46:13.190 --> 00:46:13.740
Don't plan.

00:46:26.960 --> 00:46:28.340
One more deep breath in.

00:46:32.720 --> 00:46:36.750
Keeping your eyes
closed, exhale.

00:46:36.750 --> 00:46:39.920
Now bring your awareness
to the top of your head.

00:46:44.224 --> 00:46:46.390
Focus all of your attention
on the top of your head.

00:46:49.282 --> 00:46:53.030
Now bring your awareness
down to your forehead.

00:46:58.040 --> 00:47:00.196
Center your awareness in
between your eyebrows.

00:47:05.930 --> 00:47:09.950
Now take a look
inward into your mind,

00:47:09.950 --> 00:47:11.680
and become an
observer of your mind.

00:47:22.760 --> 00:47:25.740
Bring your awareness
to your eyes.

00:47:25.740 --> 00:47:27.050
Relax the muscles in your eyes.

00:47:39.490 --> 00:47:42.610
Bring your awareness down to
your mouth and tongue and jaw.

00:47:42.610 --> 00:47:45.220
Relax the muscles in your jaw.

00:47:45.220 --> 00:47:46.030
Relax your tongue.

00:47:46.030 --> 00:47:48.238
Let your tongue slip down
to the bottom of the mouth.

00:48:02.212 --> 00:48:04.420
Bring your awareness down
to your neck and shoulders.

00:48:10.592 --> 00:48:12.550
Release the tension in
your neck and shoulders.

00:48:12.550 --> 00:48:14.090
Let your shoulders drop down.

00:48:24.010 --> 00:48:28.395
Now bring your awareness
down to your heart.

00:48:28.395 --> 00:48:30.910
And see if you can feel
the beating of your heart.

00:48:39.874 --> 00:48:42.070
When you become aware of
the beating of your heart,

00:48:42.070 --> 00:48:43.510
focus harder and see
if you can pick up

00:48:43.510 --> 00:48:44.843
on the rhythm of your heartbeat.

00:48:57.910 --> 00:48:59.840
Take a deep breath in
bringing your awareness

00:48:59.840 --> 00:49:04.070
slowly back up your body
to the top of your head.

00:49:07.910 --> 00:49:08.785
Exhale slowly.

00:49:12.194 --> 00:49:13.610
Bring your awareness
to your eyes.

00:49:17.019 --> 00:49:20.100
And slowly open your eyes.

00:49:34.530 --> 00:49:39.820
See how easy it is for
the mind to wander?

00:49:39.820 --> 00:49:41.140
Takes a few seconds actually.

00:49:41.140 --> 00:49:45.410
Within two seconds, the mind's
already on another thought.

00:49:45.410 --> 00:49:47.240
And many of our
thoughts that we have

00:49:47.240 --> 00:49:48.985
are unrelated to each other.

00:49:48.985 --> 00:49:53.050
It's like a pinball
machine in there.

00:49:53.050 --> 00:49:57.654
And like anything, if you
exercise the mind regularly,

00:49:57.654 --> 00:49:58.570
it'll become stronger.

00:49:58.570 --> 00:50:01.731
If you work out once
a year, not much good.

00:50:01.731 --> 00:50:03.230
Work out regularly,
become stronger.

00:50:03.230 --> 00:50:04.884
Your stamina increases.

